            <div class="x6 last">
                <div>
                    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0;">Golf &mdash;</h3>
                    <p>Cambrian Heights' golf lovers have the luxury of staying close to several golf courses. <strong>Confederation Park Golf Course</strong> is a nine-hole, par-three public golf course and the closest. The course offers country skiing in winter and hosts the Lions Club Christmas Lights Display through the Christmas season.</p>
                    <p>If you are willing to drive a bit farther, you will find <strong>Silver Springs Golf & Country Club</strong> on Varsity Estate Drive NW. This is a championship par 72 golf course and one of the finest in its category.</p>
                    <p>The <strong>Winston Golf Club</strong> is a well-kept golf course on 6th Street NE, less than a 10-minute drive from Cambrian Heights.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="margin-top: 50px;">
                    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0;">Parks &mdash;</h3>
                    <p>One of the attractions of living in Cambrian Heights is its green open spaces, pathways, and large parks. Two of Calgary's finest parks – <strong>Confederation Park</strong> and <strong>Nose Hill Park</strong>, are minutes away from the neighbourhood.</p>
                    <p><strong>Confederation Park</strong> is one of the area's largest parks, covering over 400 acres. It's a clean, well-maintained urban park with gigantic trees, offering visitors a wide range of activities. Winter sports like cross country skiing and sledding are popular here as the park sits on an elevated area. In summer, visitors use the tennis courts, picnic tables, ball diamonds, BBQ facilities, cycling paths, and hiking trails. It's a park for the entire family. A running brook makes for an ideal spot to spend a morning.</p>
                    <p><strong>Nose Hill Park</strong> is a natural park and one of Calgary's most precious parks. The park is lush with native grasslands and prairie wildlife. Coyotes and deer can roam the grasslands, and several species of voles and mice are seen here. The park is home to porcupines, Richardson's ground squirrels, and pocket gophers. The park has over eight kilometres of paved walkway trails, hiking trails, and dedicated off-leash areas. Set on a hill, the park offers scenic views of The Rocky Mountains and Bow River Valley.</p>
                    <p><strong>Cambrian Heights Park</strong> on Northmount Drive NW and Coleridge Rd NW Playground are two playgrounds for Cambrian Heights toddlers and young children.</p>
                    <p>For dogs, there is the <strong>Cambrian Heights Off-Leash Area</strong> on Cardiff Drive NW and Collingwood Off-Leash Area in neighbouring Collingwood.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="margin-top: 50px;">
                    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0;">Shopping &mdash;</h3>
                    <p><strong>Market Mall</strong> – one of Calgary's largest indoor malls is located in the neighbourhood of Varsity. The mall is less than a 10-minute drive from Cambrian Heights and houses over 200 retailers, restaurants, and services. It's the perfect mall for the entire family and has a playground for children. From apparel, footwear, and jewellery to electronics, books, home furnishings, and more – you can find it all here.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="margin-top: 50px;">
                    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0;">Fitness &mdash;</h3>
                    <p><strong>The Calgary Winter Club</strong> – one of the city's high-end fitness facilities, is located on 14th Street NW - just a four-minute drive from Cambrian Heights. This private recreation club has several amenities, and you will find several activities to get fit and healthy. There are several opportunities for children as well, including a rock-climbing wall. Other activities include tennis, curling, squash, skating, and swimming.</p>
                </div>
                <div style="margin-top: 50px;">
                    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0;">Restaurants and bars &mdash;</h3>
                    <p>As a Cambrian Heights resident, you have a ton of options for restaurants and bars. Some must-try places include <strong>Puspa Restaurant</strong>, <strong>PHO HOLIC Vietnamese Bistro</strong>, and <strong>Manna Korean Cuisine</strong>.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
